message.body: Whats up? Im in aburn with erin running errands!

It's about to get crazy over here.
But we won't eat til 6:30 or so!!
Ok im at ac moore. I will text you after and see if youre free
What are you up to Friday? Everyone just arrived, thinking tonight be too much. I have a car all day Friday
Ok that works!! Im just going to shopping. im still with the frame lady!
Okay. Sorry I always get ambushed the night I get here
KIT Friday Leah and I will be out and about.
Happy thanksgiving! I am thankful to have you as my BFF for reals.
Haha i am even more thankful to have the funniest girl in the world as my bff! Have fun! Im waiting for santa in the macys parade!
